<s> HyTime considers links and locators to be seperate constructs.  </s>
<s> locators are  </s>
<s> pass-through in that if you point at it, you are effectively pointing at what it points at (ad infinitum).  </s>
<s> hyperlinks are normal SGML elements in terms of pointing at them.  </s>
<s> If you point at a link you are pointing at the element which defines that link.  </s>
<s> (whether the element "knows" it is the definition of a link is another question....)  </s>
